OL,3,CHigh Court rules removing low traffic
OL,4,Czones in Tower Hamlets was lawful
OL,6,FThe High Court has ruled that the
OL,7,Fremoval of three Low Traffic
OL,8,FNeighbourhoods (LTNs) in Tower Hamlets
OL,9,Fis lawful.
OL,11,FThe campaign group Save Our Safer
OL,12,FStreets (SOSS) took Lutfur Rahman, the
OL,13,FMayor of Tower Hamlets, to the High
OL,14,FCourt, accusing him of unlawfully
OL,15,Ftrying to get rid of the LTNs last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FRahman's successful legal challenge
OL,19,Fmeans that the controversial schemes
OL,20,Fto control traffic in east London will
OL,21,Fbe axed.
