OL,6,FRahman said: "I welcome the High
OL,7,FCourt's ruling that the Council
OL,8,Ffollowed the proper procedures.
OL,10,F"We had a responsibility to fulfil the
OL,11,Fdemocratic mandate from voters in the
OL,12,FMay 2022 election to reopen these
OL,13,Fthree roads, and we also held further
OL,14,Fconsultations to ensure the views of
OL,15,Fall affected residents were considered.
