OL,6,F"While LTNs improve air quality in
OL,7,Ftheir immediate vicinity, the previous
OL,8,FLabour administration's botched
OL,9,Fimplementation of LTNs in Tower
OL,10,FHamlets caused traffic congestion on
OL,11,Fmain roads.
OL,13,F"This led to complaints about
OL,14,Fincreased air pollution and negative
OL,15,Fimpacts on the health of many who live
OL,16,Fon main roads, which are predominantly
OL,17,Fworking-class households."
