OL,3,CHigh Court rules removing low traffic
OL,4,Czones in Tower Hamlets was lawful
OL,6,FJane Harris from SOSS said: "The Low
OL,7,FTraffic Neighbourhoods are a major
OL,8,Fsuccess story in a deprived area of
OL,9,FLondon, virtually eliminating serious
OL,10,Froad injuries and improving air
OL,11,Fquality inside and outside the schemes.
OL,13,F"We believed that there were serious
OL,14,Fflaws in the way the Mayor decided to
OL,15,Fremove them. We remain convinced that
OL,16,Fthe Mayor of Tower Hamlets' proposal
OL,17,Fwill be expensive, unpopular, harmful
OL,18,Fto residents' health and safety, and
OL,19,Fit will jeopardise the Mayor of
OL,20,FLondon's transport strategy."
