OL,3,CHigh Court rules removing low traffic
OL,4,Czones in Tower Hamlets was lawful
OL,6,FIn light of today's verdict,
OL,7,Fcampaigners have warned that the
OL,8,Fcourt's decision could have broader
OL,9,Fimplications for similar traffic
OL,10,Fschemes across the capital.
OL,12,FThe campaign group has until January
OL,13,Fto decide whether or not they want to
OL,14,Fput in an application to the Court of
OL,15,FAppeal and they are now asking for
OL,16,Fpeople to join their campaign.
